725108f-a.text:
20th Road, east from 46th Street, showing part of the former Old Bowery Bay Road, which was a zigzagging dirt road leading into Newtown. View 2 shows farmland along the south side of the road and view 3 a hollow along the north side.

P. L. Sperr        May 27, 1934
Views 1, 2, 3
